rows.label: qev025703_MSG0001
rows.name:
Yes yes? Can I help you? Nondisclosure agreements
keep me from discussing work, but I'm happy to speak
about anything else, probably?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025703_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask what sort of work Aalis does.

rows.label: qev025703_MSG0002
rows.name:
You want measurements of my body's physical
dimensions, yes?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025703_MSG0003
rows.name:
As it turns out, all of my biometrics were taken when I
started work at my current job. You are welcome to a
copy of that data, if you want?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025703_MSG0004
rows.name:
I won't ask what you aim to do with these numbers,
okay? ...All right, yes I will.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025703_MSG0005
rows.name:
Wonder-ware, you say? Wonder...ware?
This is some new manner of weapon, perhaps?
It sounds so so deadly.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025703_MSG0006
rows.name:
I don't know the specifics, but but but I wish you luck
in your R&D efforts![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025703_MSG0007
rows.name:
I am employed as an engineer at a company making
Skell armaments, you see?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025703_MSG0008
rows.name:
I'm afraid anything more than that is classified, isn't it?
Very very secret.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025703_MSG0009
rows.name:
Ever since coming to this city, Panyar has been going
on about fashion battles and runway wars, hasn't she?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025703_MSG0010
rows.name: Is that "wonder-ware" of yours a part of all this?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025703_MSG0011
rows.name:
I hope no one has died during the development of your
ultimate wonder-ware weapon?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025703_MSG0012
rows.name:
I asked a coworker about it, and she explained that a
single look is enough to incapacitate a human male?
What an instrument of of of carnage![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025703_MSG0013
rows.name:
...Oh? It failed in trials? I am sorry, yes? So so sorry.
Though perhaps it was too powerful a weapon to
unleash on the world.[ST:wait ]
